data.description: Charming Ranch Style Single Family Home, Chattahoochee exterior (front) siding (rear). On top of small hill, private backyard terraces, 2 huge Oak Trees. Screened in front porch, lot's of room, 2236 sq ft under air, 2551 total sq ft total, including converted garage and 10x16 attached shed (all permitted!) Complete A/C less than 2 years old. All this and more in very desirable Jensen Beach just minutes from downtown. MOTIVATED SELLER.. Home needs some up-dates. Lots' of up-side.
